#. Description of the plugin
#: cf7-ai-copilot.php
msgid "Adds an AI Inbox to your Contact Form 7 forms: every submission gets an AI-drafted summary, suggested reply, category, priority, and confidence score for you to review and send — nothing is ever emailed automatically. Uses your own OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, or OpenRouter API key."
msgstr ""

